description:
This is a 22 minute workout called '20 minute Cycling Workout for Beginners' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a 20 min indoor cycling workout for beginners! If you just got your spinning bike, exercise bike, or stationary bike, THIS IS FOR YOU!
